I damn care what people think about this song but I believe this is best second song from Coke Studio after “Tajdare Haram”. #AtifAslam & #GulPanra did it very nicely with two different languages & the beats are incredible, Especially the beats of “Rabab” in the beginning of the song. No one can beat him in any way. One word for this song “#Behtreen” :)
" Request for @Coke studio pls one more song from Gul Panra in Urdu " TY Cheers :)
